#: templates/instances/index.html:32
msgid "Quotes about West Pier, Brighton"
msgstr "來自Brighton 有關西岸碼頭的引述"

#: templates/instances/index.html:35
msgid "SayIt containing individual quotes about West Pier in Brighton"
msgstr "SayIt 包括來自Brighton 有關西岸碼頭的個別引述"

#: templates/instances/index.html:42
msgid "For councils and organisations that hold public&nbsp;meetings"
msgstr "讓地方政府與在地組織可以舉公開集會　"

#: templates/instances/index.html:43
msgid ""
"Still publishing meeting transcripts on PDFs? SayIt makes it easier for your "
"readers to find the parts that really interest them."
msgstr ""
"仍使用PDF 檔案整理會議發言記錄? SayIt 讓你的讀者更方便找出他們感興趣的資訊"

#: templates/instances/index.html:44
msgid ""
"Unlike crusty old PDFs, SayIt works beautifully on every device from a phone "
"to a tablet to a desktop. And it’s accessible for screenreaders and "
"assistive devices."
msgstr ""
"不像惱人的PDF檔案，從手機到桌機，SayIt在任何平台上都能完美呈現，而且它對輔　"
"助機具與螢幕閱讀的可親性也很高。　"

#: templates/instances/index.html:45
msgid "The Leveson Inquiry transcripts"
msgstr "Leveson事件調查的文件抄本"

#: templates/instances/index.html:48
msgid "Screenshot of the SayIt speech editing interface"
msgstr "SayIt發言編輯的螢幕截圖"

#: templates/instances/index.html:55
msgid "For researchers, historians, and&nbsp;journalists"
msgstr "歷史學者，研究人員與新聞記者的用途"

#: templates/instances/index.html:56
msgid "Forget those dusty folders – SayIt organises your interviews for you."
msgstr "忘了那些老舊的檔案櫃吧，SayIt幫助你整理你做過的採訪　"

#: templates/instances/index.html:57
msgid ""
"Search by keyword, across your entire canon or within just one interview. "
"Browse by date, speaker or segment. Link to and share one statement, or "
"entire interviews, with ease."
msgstr ""
"透過關鍵字可搜尋整個資料庫或單一訪談。可依日期，講者或部門瀏覧，方便容易地連"
"結或分享某一個聲明或整個訪談。"

#: templates/instances/index.html:58
msgid "The Nixon Watergate tapes"
msgstr "尼克森水門案錄音帶　"

#: templates/instances/index.html:61
msgid "President Nixon’s profile page in the Watergate Tapes SayIt"
msgstr "尼克森總統在SayIt上的檔案頁－水門案錄音帶"

#: templates/instances/index.html:67
msgid "And lots, lots more!"
msgstr "還有更多更多"

#: templates/instances/index.html:68
msgid ""
"SayIt isn’t just for work: it’s for anyone who wants to collect statements "
"on any subject, or publish any form of spoken word."
msgstr ""
"SayIt不只用於工作，它還可以用來收集任何主題之言論或是出版任何形式之發言"

#: templates/instances/index.html:69
msgid ""
"From wartime love-letters to local history projects, SayIt is a wonderful, "
"easy-access way to organise transcripts."
msgstr "從戰時的情書到當地文史計畫，SayIt 是一個完美，好用的方式來保存文字副本"

#: templates/instances/index.html:70
msgid "The complete works of Shakespeare"
